    • fromString

      public static Card fromString(String s)
      Returns a Card enum given a String.

      The String can be the short 2 character name or the name of the enum constant. Leading or trailing whitespace is ignored and the case does not matter.

      Parameters:
      s - String that represents the card name
      Returns:
      Card enum that is represented by the String
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if a Card can not be parsed from the String
      NullPointerException - if the argument is null

      public static List<Card> fullDeck()
